sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant PlatformIngress as Platform Ingress<br/>(kube-rbac-proxy / oauth-proxy)
    participant RestProxy as rest-proxy Sidecar<br/>8008/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh gRPC Server<br/>8033/TCP gRPC

    Note over Client, ModelMesh: Flow 1: REST Inference Request

    Client->>PlatformIngress: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (platform-level)
    PlatformIngress->>RestProxy: Forward request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8008/TCP<br/>Configurable TLS
    Note right of RestProxy: CustomJSONPb unmarshals JSON<br/>Handles tensor types:<br/>BOOL, INT8-64, UINT8-64,<br/>FP16-64, BYTES<br/>Supports nested arrays &<br/>base64-encoded data
    RestProxy->>ModelMesh: ModelInfer RPC<br/>gRPC/8033/TCP<br/>Configurable TLS (localhost)
    Note right of ModelMesh: ModelMesh performs<br/>model inference
    ModelMesh-->>RestProxy: InferResponse (protobuf)
    Note right of RestProxy: CustomJSONPb marshals<br/>protobuf to JSON<br/>Converts raw binary<br/>contents to typed arrays
    RestProxy-->>PlatformIngress: JSON Response<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    PlatformIngress-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client, ModelMesh: Flow 2: Model Metadata Request

    Client->>PlatformIngress: GET /v2/models/{name}<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (platform-level)
    PlatformIngress->>RestProxy: Forward request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8008/TCP
    RestProxy->>ModelMesh: ModelMetadata RPC<br/>gRPC/8033/TCP
    ModelMesh-->>RestProxy: ModelMetadataResponse (protobuf)
    RestProxy-->>PlatformIngress: JSON Response
    PlatformIngress-->>Client: JSON Model Metadata
